Uses of Class
gameboard.objects.MovingObject

Packages that use MovingObject
Package Description
datastorage
This package contains the methods for the data storage process by using the Maven dependencies and integrating JSON-B.
gameboard.objects
This package deals with all the objects, with which you can move over the gameboard and which are needed to play this game.
gui.controller
This package contains the controller classes like SceneController and MovingObjectController.
gui.view
This package contains the classes that implement the stage and the different scenes and panes.
simulator
This package contains the classes to start and store the main information of the game.
